{
  "entries": [
    {
      "offset": "0x6d6d8",
      "back_en": "Never in life have I breathed air so fetid as that",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Faithful; archaic tone preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d70d",
      "back_en": "that chills my very bones in this place...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d791",
      "back_en": "This brings to memory a dire/funereal scroll that",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'most unseemly' (improper) shifted to 'funesto' (dire) and moved from memory to scroll."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d7c3",
      "back_en": "I once read with great fear.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'darkling' carried implicitly; acceptable."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d7ed",
      "back_en": "It was the tale of a man wandering in a forest",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d820",
      "back_en": "such as this, when he met a woman of",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d852",
      "back_en": "unmatched beauty.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d85d",
      "back_en": "But behold, beneath this woman's mask",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'of deception' implied by context/next line."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d891",
      "back_en": "a nugwisomkami was hidden! Which feasts upon the",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate; term preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d8c6",
      "back_en": "flesh of travelers.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6d924",
      "back_en": "Does the tale not frighten you, Master Haku?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate, formal voice kept."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6dde1",
      "back_en": "What do you mean?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Idiomatic equivalent."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6de35",
      "back_en": "G-Good heavens, Master Haku, do not make such",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'Gadzooks' rendered idiomatically."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6de65",
      "back_en": "jests! This is no matter for laughter!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6df29",
      "back_en": "O-One must agree...",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Close equivalent."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6df44",
      "back_en": "She possesses some charm, but no. Milady is not",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6df77",
      "back_en": "beautiful enough that such creatures",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'fell' (evil) dropped but minor."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6dfa3",
      "back_en": "could pass themselves off as.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6dfb0",
      "back_en": "In truth, let us praise thy simplicity, oh lady...",
      "verdict": "revise",
      "note": "'homeliness' (plainness/ugliness, an insult) softened to 'simplicidade'; added 'ó dama'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6e28b",
      "back_en": "Eeek! Wh-Wh-What manner of--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6e347",
      "back_en": "M-Master Haku...!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6e89c",
      "back_en": "I-I... I-I-I--",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x6e90d",
      "back_en": "O-Oh, Master Haku...!",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x708da",
      "back_en": "Wh-What magic is in those ropes!?",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "'bewitcheth' rendered as 'magia há'; meaning preserved."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x70d0a",
      "back_en": "M-Master Ukon! I beg you, speak the truth! I knew nothing",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate; 'Prithee' rendered as 'Peço que'."
    },
    {
      "offset": "0x70d3f",
      "back_en": "of these plans.",
      "verdict": "pass",
      "note": "Accurate."
    }
  ],
  "reviewed": 26
}